    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle, then soak 1 <strong>lasagne sheet </strong>per person in <strong>boiled water </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong>, then top, tail, peel and finely dice your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Remove the base of your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then wash under <strong>cold running water</strong> and cut away the core, then pat dry with kitchen paper and tear the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> from the stem until you are left with a pile of leaves (set these aside for later!)</p>",
