    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped onion </strong>and<strong> diced carrot </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4 min or until softened</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1695738574679-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1695738574679-x400.jpg",
