          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1695738578883-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan with the <strong>remaining lasagne sheets </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium, and cook for a initial 7 min, stirring occasionally – this is your <strong>pasta mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695738582880-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695738582880-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
