          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695738586869-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, remove from the heat, add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> béchamel</strong></p><p>After an initial 7 min, top the <strong>pasta mixture</strong> with the <strong>béchamel </strong>(reserve the pan!) and cook for 3-4 min further or until the sauce has reduced and the pasta and mince are cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>stove top lasagne</strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>soaked lasagne sheets</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1695738589972-x200.jpg",
